  "title": "[Healthcare Roles, Min 3 Months] Pharmacy Assistant / Admin / Patient Service (Min A levels) #HCY",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for motivated individuals to support day-to-day operations in a healthcare setting. Training will be provided.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist pharmacists with dispensing preparations (labelling, packing, sorting medications)</p></li><li><p>Provide frontline patient service, including registration, queue management, and enquiry handling</p></li><li><p>Perform administrative duties such as data entry, filing, and updating patient records</p></li><li><p>Manage inventory: stock-taking, replenishment, and storage of medical supplies</p></li><li><p>Ensure accuracy, confidentiality, and compliance with healthcare regulations</p></li><li><p>Support the smooth workflow of the pharmacy or clinic operations</p></li><li><p>Work closely with healthcare professionals to deliver quality service to patients<br /><br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>Minimum GCE A Levels / Diploma</p><p>No experience required; training will be provided</p><p>WA me at <a href=\"http://wa.me/+6598326219\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://wa.me/+6598326219</a> or tele me at <a href=\"https://t.me/sallytsin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@sallytsin</a></p><p>For interested candidates, please send your most recent and updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:sallytsin@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">sallytsin@recruitexpress.com.sg<br /><br /></a></p><p>Tsin Chien Yee Sally<br />R25127272<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA License No. 99C4599</p>",
